In a Car hire system which of these would be a good domain class?
Car
Car hire service
Add Customer
Purchase new car
Correct. A car would be an important domain area of the system.  The others all look like use cases, as they are doing something to things.



The correct answer is a car, as this would be an important domain area of the system.  The others all look like use cases, as they are doing something to things.
